            "text": "Catalister's AI is trained on real e-commerce conversion and SEO data, not general web text. This means its product descriptions are optimized for actual sales performance and search rankings—not just readable copy. It also handles bulk generation, supplier data matching, and Shopify publishing in one workflow.",
